snippet.title: Cards Survivors - Steam Next Fest 2023 Demo
snippet.description:
Cards Survivors is a unique mix of card games, action games and roguelikes. Craft a unique deck, slay hordes of enemies, discover cards of immense power and survive as long as you can.

Cards Survivors (C) Family Devs
Coming to Steam on Q4 2023
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2338040/Cards_Survivors/

#steamnextfest #steam #steamgames #steamgame #cardssurvivors
